extends layout

block content
  section#about
    h2 About Us
    p At Crimson Academy, we believe in the power of knowledge and innovation. We are dedicated to providing top-notch courses that empower students, professionals, and lifelong learners to master new skills and excel in their careers. Our platform is built by experts passionate about education, ensuring that every learner gets the best experience possible.

  section#mission
    h3 Our Mission
    p We strive to bridge the gap between education and industry needs by offering comprehensive, hands-on courses. Our goal is to create a learning ecosystem that fosters curiosity, creativity, and career success. Whether you want to break into a new field or sharpen your existing skills, we are here to support your journey.

  section#why-choose-us
    h2 Why Choose Us?
    .reasons-container
      .reason
        h3 Expert Instructors
        p Learn from industry professionals with real-world experience who are passionate about helping you succeed.
      .reason
        h3 Flexible Learning
        p Access courses anytime, anywhere, with self-paced and live learning options to fit your schedule.
      .reason
        h3 Career Support
        p Gain practical skills, resume guidance, and job placement assistance to kickstart your career.

  section#team
    h2 Meet Our Team
    .team-container
      .team-slider
        each member in team
          .team-member
            img(src=member.image, alt=member.name)
            h3= member.name
            p= member.role

  script.
    let index = 0;
    function slideTeam() {
      const slider = document.querySelector(".team-slider");
      index = (index + 1) % team.length;
      slider.style.transform = `translateX(-${index * 100}%)`;
    }
    setInterval(slideTeam, 2000);

